{"tid":2178469,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk確認Tesla的內華達廠房曾為網絡攻擊目標   黑客承諾酬金100萬美元","createTime":"2020-08-28T11:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T01:45:03.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3140f759cf8dfcff493624156f46cd11c7fc5051","tid":2178469,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"特斯拉(Tesla)創辦人馬斯克(Elon Musk)證實，位於美國內華達州的特斯拉工廠遭到網絡攻擊，形容這是一次嚴重襲擊。<br />\n<br />\nTeslarati早前報道稱，特斯拉超級工廠(Gigafactory)的一名僱員此前幫助美國聯邦調查局挫敗一名俄羅斯男子(Kriuchkov) 的網絡攻擊計劃，該男子已在8月22日被捕，並被指控蓄意破壞受保護的電腦。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部聲明指出，一名27歲男子曾試圖招募未具名公司的一名員工，計劃把惡意軟件植入特斯拉的電腦系統，並承諾向該名員工支付酬金100萬美元。該軟件旨在從網絡中提取數據，並向特斯拉勒索贖金。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，該名員工及後向特斯拉報告，特斯拉隨後向美國聯邦調查局(FBI)報案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.teslarati.com/tesla-employee-fbi-thwarts-russian-cybersecurity-attack/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teslarati.com%2Ftesla-employee-fbi-thwarts-russian-cybersecurity-attack%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyM1lVRHyxjHm7NpFearlrcU%3D&h=f8b0da0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.teslarati.com/tesla-employee-fbi-thwarts-russian-cybersecurity-attack/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=606795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D606795&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyM1lVRHyxjHm7NpFearlrcU%3D&h=0c2696d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=606795</a>"},{"pid":"ab740fe52ca6bd21925febcc4b9ca140b6ce552b","tid":2178469,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T22:58:45.000Z","msg":"Gta5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580ca60761f4c992f03e853771ffc37fc1279b84","tid":2178469,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab740fe52ca6bd21925febcc4b9ca140b6ce552b","tid":2178469,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T22:58